'''肖恩·L·S·多诺万'''（{{lang-en|Shaun L.S. Donovan}}，{{bd|1966年|1月24日||}}），前[[美国住房及城市发展部|美国住房及城市发展部]]长，第44任[[美國總統|美國總統]][[巴拉克·奥巴马|巴拉克·奥巴马]]第一任内阁閣员之一。

== 簡介 ==
在擔任部长之前，他任[[纽约市|纽约市]][[房屋发展部|房屋发展部]]部长。

奥巴马在2008年12月13日出席广播节目时，宣布打算任命多诺万。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://change.gov/newsroom/entry/secretary_of_housing_and_urban_development_announced_in_weekly_address/ |title=Secretary of Housing and Urban Development announced in Weekly Address |publisher=[[change.gov|change.gov]] |date=December 13, 2008 |language=en |accessdate=December 14, 2008 |archive-date=2016-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027194750/http://change.gov/newsroom/entry/secretary_of_housing_and_urban_development_announced_in_weekly_address/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=swornin>{{cite web |author = Staff |title = Shaun Donovan Secretary U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development |publisher = Department of Housing and Urban Development |date = 2009-01-29 |url = http://www.hud.gov/about/secretary/donovanbio.cfm |format =  |accessdate = 2009-01-30 |quote = On January 26, 2009, Shaun Donovan was sworn in as the 15th United States Secretary for Housing and Urban Development. |language = en |archive-date = 2016-08-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160829092854/http://www.hud.gov/about/secretary/donovanbio.cfm |dead-url = no }}</ref>

2010年1月，歐巴馬總統率領閣員到國會發表[[國情諮文|國情諮文]]期間，肖恩·多諾萬被指定為[[指定倖存者|指定倖存者]]（{{lang|en|Designated survivor}}）在一處秘密安全地點待命，以便在聚集在眾議院會議廳中的總統、副總統以及其他的官員面臨災難時，能按照[[美國總統繼任順序|美國總統繼任順序]]繼任總統職位。

